About

Jeroen is a Senior Data Scientist at YPlan in New York City. He has an M.Sc. in Artificial Intelligence and a Ph.D. in Machine Learning. Jeroen enjoys biking the Brooklyn Bridge, building tools, and eating stroopwafels. He doesn't always tweet, but when he does it's about (data) science, machine learning, data visualization, or a new post.
